Dear valued customer,

Thank you for your inquiry regarding your recent claim. I am pleased to inform you that our investigation has concluded, and we are writing to provide you with an update on the status of your claim.

After thorough review, our team has determined that your claim is eligible for [insert relevant details, e.g., partial or full reimbursement]. We will be processing your payment within the next [insert timeframe, e.g., 7-10 business days] and will send a confirmation email once the payment has been made.

In the meantime, if you have any further questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to reach out to us. We are committed to providing you with exceptional service and appreciate your patience and understanding.

Thank you for choosing [insert company name]. We value your business and look forward to serving you in the future.

Sincerely,
[Your Name]
Senior Customer Service Representative
</OUTPUT_TEXT>
